---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ローフードとは｜ベーシック・マイスター資格講座 | &LAB TOKYO 東京・渋谷</title>
  <meta name="description" content="ローフード本格資格講座。ローフードベーシック（2級・準1級）・マイスタープレミアムコース（1級）。東京・渋谷またはオンライン。ELLE gourmet認定・安藤千英が指導。日本リビングビューティー協会認定校。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    /* ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
       レイアウト崩れ防止の最重要ルール
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ */
    html, body {
      overflow-x: hidden;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0; padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --linen:  #FBFBFA;
      --linen-2:#F4F2EE;
      --linen-3:#EAE7E0;
      --sumi:   #1C1C1A;
      --sumi-2: #2A2A27;
      --ink:    #1C1C1A;
      --ink-2:  #3D3D38;
      --ink-3:  #7A7A72;
      --green:  #A9D159;
      --green-d:#7AAF2A;
      --divider:#D8D4CC;
      --f-s:    'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      --f-b:    'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      /* コンテナ幅 */
      --max-w:  1040px;
      --pad:    clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--f-b);
      background: var(--linen);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.8;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ━━ コンテナ（全セクション共通） ━━ */
    .wrap {
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--pad);
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ━━ Nav ━━ */
    nav {
      position: fixed; inset: 0 0 auto 0; z-index: 500;
      height: 52px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 var(--pad);
      background: rgba(28,28,26,.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,.08);
    }
    .nav-logo img { height: 30px; width: auto; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(244,242,238,.6); text-decoration: none; padding: 0 .8rem; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: var(--green); }
    .nav-cta { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block; background: var(--green); color: var(--sumi); padding: .4rem 1rem; margin-left: .8rem; text-decoration: none; transition: background .2s; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--green-d); color: #fff; }

    /* ━━ Hero ━━ */
    .hero {
      margin-top: 52px;
      position: relative;
      height: 65vh; min-height: 440px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
    }
    .hero-img { position: absolute; inset: 0; }
    .hero-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 30%; display: block; }
    .hero-img::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(28,28,26,.9) 0%, rgba(28,28,26,.35) 55%, rgba(28,28,26,.05) 100%);
    }
    .hero-body {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      width: 100%; padding: var(--pad);
      padding-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }
    .hero-body-inner { max-width: 640px; }
    .eyebrow-sm { font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; line-height: 1.4; color: #F4F2EE; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .hero-sub { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: clamp(.9rem, 1.5vw, 1rem); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: .06em; color: rgba(244,242,238,.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.9; }
    .hero-badges { display: flex; gap: .5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .badge { font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 500; padding: .35rem .8rem; border: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,.25); color: rgba(244,242,238,.6); white-space: nowrap; }
    .btn-sumi { display: inline-block; background: var(--linen); color: var(--sumi); font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .06em; padding: .9rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s; }
    .btn-sumi:hover { background: var(--green); }

    /* ━━ 共通セクション ━━ */
    .sec { padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .eyebrow { font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green-d); display: block; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .sec-h2 { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .rule { width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--divider); margin: 1.6rem 0 2.4rem; }
    .body-p { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 2.1; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .body-p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ━━ とは解説（2列→1列） ━━ */
    .what-sec { background: var(--linen-2); }
    .what-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .what-img img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
    .what-points { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .what-points li { display: flex; gap: .8rem; font-size: .88rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.8; }
    .what-points li::before { content: '—'; color: var(--green-d); flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700; }

    /* ━━ 効果（墨色・3列→レスポンシブ） ━━ */
    .benefits-sec { background: var(--sumi); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .benefits-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 2px; margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .benefit { background: rgba(244,242,238,.04); padding: 2rem 1.6rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,.08); }
    .benefit-num { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(169,209,89,.3); display: block; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .benefit h4 { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #F4F2EE; margin-bottom: .6rem; }
    .benefit p { font-size: .82rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.48); line-height: 1.9; }

    /* ━━ コース ━━ */
    .courses-sec { background: var(--linen); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .course-card { margin-top: 3rem; }
    .course-header {
      background: var(--sumi); padding: 2rem 2.4rem;
    }
    .course-header-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .course-badge { font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green); display: block; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    .course-h3 { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; color: #F4F2EE; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .course-tagline { font-size: .82rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.5); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 480px; }
    .price-box { text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price-label { font-size: .65rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.38); display: block; margin-bottom: .2rem; letter-spacing: .06em; }
    .price-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: .5rem; justify-content: flex-end; margin-bottom: .2rem; }
    .price-type { font-size: .7rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.4); }
    .price-num { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--green); }
    .price-note { font-size: .65rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.3); display: block; margin-top: .2rem; }

    .course-body { background: var(--linen-2); padding: 2rem 2.4rem; }
    .course-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .col-title { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .curriculum-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .6rem; }
    .curriculum-list li { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.75; padding-left: 1rem; position: relative; }
    .curriculum-list li::before { content: '・'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--green-d); }
    .info-table { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .6rem; }
    .info-row { display: flex; gap: .8rem; font-size: .82rem; }
    .info-l { color: var(--ink-3); min-width: 70px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 500; font-size: .78rem; }
    .info-v { color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; }

    .course-action { background: var(--linen-3); padding: 1.4rem 2.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
    .course-action-text { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--ink-3); flex: 1; }
    .btn-apply { display: inline-block; background: var(--sumi); color: #F4F2EE; font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .06em; padding: .8rem 1.6rem; text-decoration: none; transition: background .2s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .btn-apply:hover { background: var(--sumi-2); }

    /* ━━ こんな方へ ━━ */
    .whom-sec { background: var(--linen-2); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .whom-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 2px; margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .whom-item { background: var(--linen); padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem; }
    .whom-item h4 { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: .6rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }
    .whom-item p { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--ink-3); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* ━━ 講師 ━━ */
    .instructor-sec { background: var(--linen); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .instructor-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
    .instructor-img img { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover; object-position: top; display: block; }
    .instructor-cap { font-size: .7rem; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: .5rem; text-align: center; letter-spacing: .08em; }

    /* ━━ 受講生の声 ━━ */
    .testi-sec { background: var(--linen-2); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .testi-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 2px; margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    .testi { background: var(--linen); padding: 2rem 1.8rem; }
    .testi-q { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .9rem; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.95; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
    .testi-q::before { content: '"'; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--green-d); line-height: .6; display: block; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .testi-name { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }
    .testi-role { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: .25rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ━━ FAQ ━━ */
    .faq-sec { background: var(--linen); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .faq-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--linen-3); padding: 1.6rem 0; }
    .faq-q { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: .8rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .faq-q::before { content: 'Q. '; color: var(--green-d); }
    .faq-a { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 2; padding-left: 1.2rem; }

    /* ━━ 1Day体験ブロック（最下部・控えめ） ━━ */
    .trial-block {
      background: var(--sumi-2);
      padding: 4rem var(--pad);
    }
    .trial-inner { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .trial-rule { width: 24px; height: 1px; background: rgba(244,242,238,.18); margin: 1.4rem auto 2rem; }
    .trial-desc { font-size: .88rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.5); line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 1.8rem; }
    .trial-price { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 1.8rem; display: block; }
    .btn-ghost { display: inline-block; border: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,.25); color: rgba(244,242,238,.65); font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .06em; padding: .8rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s; }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

    /* ━━ 埋め込みフォーム ━━ */
    .form-sec { background: var(--linen-2); padding: 5rem var(--pad); }
    .form-box { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .form-title { font-family: var(--f-s); font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
    .form-note-top { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--ink-3); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    form.contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .45rem; }
    .field label { font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink-2); letter-spacing: .04em; }
    .field label .req { color: var(--green-d); margin-left: 3px; }
    .field input, .field select, .field textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: .82rem 1rem;
      background: var(--linen);
      border: 1px solid var(--divider);
      border-radius: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .88rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
      -webkit-appearance: none;
    }
    .field input:focus, .field select:focus, .field textarea:focus { border-color: var(--green-d); background: #fff; }
    .field textarea { min-height: 110px; resize: vertical; }
    .field-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    /* メルマガチェック（将来Brevo連携用 name="newsletter" value="yes"） */
    .newsletter-wrap {
      padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
      background: rgba(169,209,89,.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(169,209,89,.2);
    }
    .check-label { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .7rem; cursor: pointer; font-size: .84rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; }
    .check-label input[type="checkbox"] { width: 15px; height: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; accent-color: var(--green-d); }
    .check-note { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: .5rem; padding-left: 22px; }
    .privacy-wrap { margin-top: .4rem; }
    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%; padding: 1rem;
      background: var(--sumi); color: #F4F2EE;
      font-family: var(--f-b); font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em;
      border: none; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--sumi-2); }
    .form-bottom-note { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--ink-3); text-align: center; margin-top: .4rem; line-height: 1.7; }

    footer { background: var(--sumi); padding: 1.8rem var(--pad); text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,.05); }
    footer p { font-size: .7rem; color: rgba(244,242,238,.22); }
    footer a { color: rgba(244,242,238,.3); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--green); }

    /* ━━ レスポンシブ ━━ */
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .nav-cta { margin-left: auto; }
      .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .what-img { display: none; }
      .course-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.8rem; }
      .instructor-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .instructor-img { max-width: 200px; }
      .field-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
      .price-box { text-align: left; }
      .course-header-inner { flex-direction: column; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      :root { --pad: 1rem; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ━━ Nav ━━ -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/logo-wide.png" alt="&LAB TOKYO" /></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/lessons">レッスン</a></li>
      <li><a href="/rawfood" class="active">ローフード</a></li>
      <li><a href="/fermentation">発酵</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">安藤千英</a></li>
      <li><a href="/blog">ブログ</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#form" class="nav-cta">申し込む</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- ━━ Hero ━━ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="/rawfood-zucchini.jpg" alt="ローフード料理" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="hero-body-inner">
        <span class="eyebrow-sm">Raw Food · &LAB TOKYO</span>
        <h1>ローフードで、<br />細胞から整える。</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">48℃以下の調理で酵素・栄養を壊さない。<br />生きた食材のチカラで、内側から美しく健やかに。</p>
        <div class="hero-badges">
          <span class="badge">日本リビングビューティー協会認定校</span>
          <span class="badge">2級・準1級・1級</span>
          <span class="badge">ELLE gourmet認定料理家が指導</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#courses" class="btn-sumi">講座の詳細を見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ━━ ① ローフードとは ━━ -->
  <section class="sec what-sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="what-grid">
        <div class="what-img">
          <img src="/hero-food.jpg" alt="ローフード料理" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">What is Raw Food</span>
          <h2 class="sec-h2">ローフードとは</h2>
          <div class="rule"></div>
          <p class="body-p">ローフード（Raw Food）とは、食材を<strong>48℃以下</strong>の温度で調理または未加熱のまま食べる食事法です。この温度以下であれば、食材本来の<strong>酵素・ビタミン・ミネラル・植物栄養素（フィトケミカル）</strong>が壊れずに保たれます。</p>
          <p class="body-p">酵素は体内での消化・代謝・細胞修復・免疫機能を担う重要な存在。&LAB TOKYOでは、ローフードを単なる「生食主義」ではなく、<strong>発酵×ローフードのクロス理論</strong>として体系的に学び、日常に取り入れるライフスタイルとして提案しています。</p>
          <ul class="what-points">
            <li>酵素・ビタミン・ミネラルを壊さずに摂取できる</li>
            <li>消化器官への負担が軽減し、体のエネルギーが上がる</li>
            <li>美肌・体重管理・疲労回復・集中力向上に効果的</li>
            <li>腸内環境が整い、免疫機能が高まる</li>
            <li>砂糖・小麦・乳製品なしでも豊かな食事が実現できる</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ━━ ② 得られるもの（墨色） ━━ -->
  <section class="benefits-sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--green)">What You'll Gain</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h2" style="color:#F4F2EE;">ローフードを学ぶと、何が変わるのか。</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
